@node "Read" "Read"
@{b}DzA@{ub} in Arexx...
You need RexxReqtools.library in Libs:...
Plus RexxMast must be running.
GUI for Packing and UnPacking Files or Directories...
Supported packers :-
 LzX, LhA, DmS and UnZip which must be in C:..(Packers not supplied).
DzA will check to see if you have the required packers in C:..
You can Pack/UnPack Files or an entire Preselected Directory.
      ((If you need more packers drop me a line...))
Made GUI as friendly as possible...
Simple to UsE.
Don't forget to enter a name for files to be packed.
                                   
                                 @{b} NOTE@{ub}
If you have any problems don't hesitate to contact me..
If You think this Script is Useful Or think it's ??? 
                         Send a postcard : @{"E-Mail" link "dcg" 0}

                                Be Seeing YoU...
                            That's it...Have Fun... @{"BACK" link "main" 0}
@endnode

